  <brief_title>Observational Cohort Study of TachoSil (TC-018-IN)</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Non-interventional, Prospective, Non-controlled Study of the Use of TachoSil in Supportive Treatment in Surgery for Improvement of Haemostasis Where Standard Techniques Are Insufficient.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
