  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients exposed to TachoSil速 of all thromboembolic events, immunological events and drug
        interactions leading to thromboembolic events or major bleeding.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All subjects, treated with TachoSil 速 by the participating physicians, will be
             registered with a set of basic data from their already existing data (i.e. no
             additional diagnostic procedures will be performed).

          -  Subjects who will provide their written informed consent to use existing data, allow
             direct access to data and data processing.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
